多人搭上唔到<br />\n<br />\n西斜 搭車呢樣又真係死症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本人乃屯門撚一名。<br />\n<br />\n1. 屯門d樓，計建築面積就6-7000。計實用就成萬蚊一呎。<br />\n2. 僻唔僻：我係正常人，要返工。住屯門已經無雷工咁撚遠，返到「屯門」仲要轉專用巴士就攰到變死狗。<br />\n3. 有朋友話，怡峰，都ok靜，兼近華都置樂，都唔錯。<br />\n4. 茵翠係高壓電纜下，未見有朋友匯報生cancer，應該唔怕。"},{"pid":"c354e2d7b341645384786c16ae9a454f7ef3e129","tid":54910,"uid":739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實 屯門住得人既樓 (4,5  百呎左右) 依家幾錢呎 ? <br />\n<br />\n利申:  唔撚識</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱望過<br />\n一般咪6-7000 <br />\n近啲市中心/豪華嘅咪迫上一皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁即係屯門 平過 將軍澳 啦 <br />\n<br />\n將軍澳好多都係過萬一呎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳方便過屯門咁多"},{"pid":"4a4a17a03fde5666c54b35b5d88b455006f0bc23","tid":54910,"uid":3573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T05:54:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱望過<br />\n一般咪6-7000 <br />\n近啲市中心/豪華嘅咪迫上一皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁即係屯門 平過 將軍澳 啦 <br />\n<br />\n將軍澳好多都係過萬一呎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳方便過屯門咁多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屯門&gt;將軍澳"},{"pid":"c9a2231134227e35c1438426677c9ce3b0585270","tid":54910,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:17:47.000Z","msg":"周圍有車出港島返工既"},{"pid":"7873a4b25252a26e8bdfad9aeb8cadb5dacee20b","tid":54910,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:57:20.000Z","msg":"LU隔離座單幢樓低水 有大露台"},{"pid":"0fefc5a7113f32dc8e3d2b8f005164e412185fc6","tid":54910,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T09:52:12.000Z","msg":"但屯門養車平，買